UNOFFICIAL community modification and is NOT provided, endorsed, or supported
by Advantech Co., Ltd. in any way. It is provided as-is, with no warranty of
any kind — use at your own risk. For official support please contact Advantech.

The original Advantech driver (versions up to 3.42.9) supports Linux kernels
2.4.x through 5.x and is unmodified in the 2.4/, 2.6/, and above_3.0/
directories.
