        (ASYNCB_CTS_FLOW, ASYNCB_CHECK_CD, ASYNC_INITIALIZED, ASYNC_NORMAL_ACTIVE,
        ASYNC_SUSPENDED hidden from kernel code since kernel 5.12);
      - Fix tty->stopped -> tty->flow.stopped (kernel 5.14);
      - Fix uart_port.timeout removed, use uart_fifo_timeout() (kernel 5.14);
      - Fix tty_port.low_latency removed (kernel 5.12);
      - Fix current->state -> __set_current_state() (kernel 5.14);
      - Fix write_room/chars_in_buffer return type int -> unsigned int (kernel 5.15);
      - Fix alloc_tty_driver -> tty_alloc_driver, put_tty_driver ->
        tty_driver_kref_put (kernel 5.15);
      - Fix PDE_DATA() removed, guard uart_proc_open/uart_proc_fops for
        kernel < 4.17 only (kernel 6.0);
      - Working copy of above_3.0 with 6.x fixes located in ecu-p1618d-driver/;

